PHP Charset Detect Extension Changelog


* 1.0.2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Thu May  5 2016
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- support detect_handledata_r for binary safe problems (libchardet >= 1.0.5)


* 1.0.1
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Wed Jan  6 2016
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- support Exception on non-oop mode
	- fixed segfault


* 1.0.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mon Dec 28 2015
by JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org>
	- version update 1.0.0
	- support over php 7
	- unsupport under php 3/4/5


